title: Fire in kitchen of Seattle home
text:
Seattle firefighters responded to a fire at Stone Avenue North and 143rd Street on Saturday morning.
The fire appeared to start in the kitchen, according to officials.
. @SeattleFire responded one alarm duplex fire at Stone Ave N & 143rd St. Fire appeared to start in the kitchen. pic.twitter.com/eWdGY08TQY
